Global -------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type            Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
| A          Class<A>        -          -             -             |
| B          Class<B>        -          -             -             |
| Bar        Class<Bar>      -          -             -             |
| Baz        Class<Baz>      -          -             -             |
| Foo        Class<Foo>      -          -             -             |
| Main       Class<Main>     -          -             -             |
| X          Class<X>        -          -             -             |
| Y          Class<Y>        -          -             -             |
| Z          Class<Z>        -          -             -             |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: A --------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type               Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| A()        Constructor<A>     -          void          -             |
| A(int)     Constructor<A>     -          int           -             |
| this       Class<A>           -          -             -             |
| x          int                -          -             -             |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: B extends A ----------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type               Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| B()        Constructor<B>     -          void          -             |
| B(int)     Constructor<B>     -          int           -             |
| this       Class<B>           -          -             -             |
| x          int                -          -             A             |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: Bar --------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol           Type                 Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| doStuff          Method               void       void          -             |
| Bar()            Constructor<Bar>     -          void          -             |
| Bar(boolean)     Constructor<Bar>     -          boolean       -             |
| this             Class<Bar>           -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

